---
title: Sausage Meatballs with Tomato Sauce and Basmati Rice
description: In this recipe, we've given one of our customer favourites, honey roasted sausages, an Italian-inspired makeover by turning them into meatballs!  Rolled into balls, and mixed together with a delicious red onion relish and  panko breadcrumbs (which holds them together) these meatballs are a great thing to cook with the kids over a lazy weekend. Combined with a veg packed sauce, and finished off with a good sprinkling of chopped parsley, we’ve covered all bases when it comes to getting fussy eaters on your side! Fast family food at its finest!
